{"tid":1738061,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[區議會選舉]11月24日區選——做問卷！防數票！","createTime":"2019-11-19T06:29:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T00:23:48.000Z","uid":326269,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"25d66fe2ef8eeccc57ce2e952e3805cff0ce4751","tid":1738061,"uid":326269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:29:40.000Z","msg":"選舉通常都會有所謂問卷調查，而做問卷調查嘅機構於2015年嘅區選被報章踢爆「疑似」為建制數票<br />\n<br />\n而<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">唔做問卷係唔可以防止到建制數票</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\nSource: <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20151122/54455653\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20151122%2F54455653&d=U%2B24RsvDmKluq6DDuV4MqrP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=54afe295\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20151122%2F54455653&h=063dc134\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20151122/54455653</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日獲准於票站外進行票站調查的機構當中，香港研究協會、香港社會監察及香港社區研究中心均曾被指與建制派有密切關係，2012年立法會選舉時更有市民號召杯葛這些票站調查。香港研究協會現任會長徐子龍雖不為人熟悉，但<strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">前會長、江蘇省政協委員蘇祉祺</span></strong>身兼「香港新一代文化協會」總幹事，該會更獲<strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">教育局局長吳克儉</span></strong>等任榮譽顧問。 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1039194\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1039194&d=U%2B24RsvDmKluq6DDuV4MqrP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=39f6c5b0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1039194&h=b6ef448d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1039194</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">剛過去的區議會選舉，選舉事務處核准了<span style=\"color: purple;\">四個機構</span>於票站範圍內進行意見調查，這四個機構分別為<strong>港大民意研究計劃，<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">香港研究協會，香港社會監察及香港社區研究中心</span></span></strong>。蘋果日報和明報都曾先後有關於即時的票站調查結果可能會被作為配票之用的報導1。蘋果日報並將港大以外的<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">其餘三者形容為「與建制派有密切關係」</span></span>。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.speakout.hk/%E6%A8%99%E7%B1%A4/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E5%8D%94%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.speakout.hk%2F%25E6%25A8%2599%25E7%25B1%25A4%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A9%25B6%25E5%258D%2594%25E6%259C%2583&d=U%2B24RsvDmKluq6DDuV4MqrP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=42fd0256\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.speakout.hk/%E6%A8%99%E7%B1%A4/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E5%8D%94%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">港人講地直頭有個Label係俾呢間機構<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n根據其中一間嘅網站入面嘅資料所得，佢個問卷調查準確度甚高<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">（我求其Cap佢所謂焦點選區嘅調查資料俾大家睇吓）</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YWPv58L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYWPv58L.png&h=9a6a879a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢喺個調查報告係咁樣寫：<br />\n焦點20個選區入面有14個選區同調查結果乎合，即係至少有<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">70%準確</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n再睇佢問卷入面所問嘅問題<br />\n1. 投票原因（知名度、政綱、背景／立場、形象、過往工作表現）<br />\n2. 選民背景資料（性別、年齡、教育程度、社會階層）<br />\n3. 上次投票取向<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bE1a6dn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbE1a6dn.png&h=5ae77637&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5hZTjyn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5hZTjyn.png&h=1229d059&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zByMEyy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzByMEyy.png&h=fe192da4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺2015年嘅數字入面對家可以計得到咩年齡層、教育程度、社會階層嘅人會偏向投邊一個黨派嘅候選人<br />\n即使唔答任何問卷都好，其實佢地都可以<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">根據外貌分析選民年齡性別</span></strong></span>，點樣都可以達到一定嘅統計紀錄<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">（雖然今年登記選民嘅人數破記錄，但對家有多年嘅數據作參考係不容忽視）</span><br />\n<br />\n所以<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>拒答唔係一個好嘅方法</strong></span><br />\n解決方法係：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">亂答</span></strong></span><br />\n佢地冇權查你身份證，姐係話你咩<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">年紀</span></span>佢唔會知<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">（性別就冇得呃喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">教育程度、社會階層、上次投票取向</span></span>對方都冇機會Check到係咪準確<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：我都係鳩睇報告並非專業，有錯歡迎大家一齊探討<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">雖然選舉並非能救全家，但兄弟爬山<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n伸延閱讀：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1725914/\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1725914/</a><br />\n[區選] 區選相關策略<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1701333/\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1701333/</a><br />\n[區選]文宣圖及相關整合"},{"pid":"085a2b712ab365d82e107f8c41c04fb2426a58f8","tid":1738061,"uid":326269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:29:54.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c0c67a5d2e1b946bba38bcdf2f0e44576fcbd40","tid":1738061,"uid":326269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:30:04.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"457725a78fe905a6d27f5d40597b60d0f1dd68fd","tid":1738061,"uid":326269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:30:18.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c676d3769c7cf1aee391a9fb774888030207c411","tid":1738061,"uid":326269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:30:28.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54f26e37e675bfcd7668c9cdf3d6e9cf988df9d5","tid":1738061,"uid":326269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:32:33.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36973c1fd3b8f6bc3659d4fa794c71213ac8599b","tid":1738061,"uid":326269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:32:43.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"797f94e446c5012f537e47a1ca3675a8b5b073a5","tid":1738061,"uid":326269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:32:53.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21813d9e4ae56c96937920a78cf0aae17b0931dc","tid":1738061,"uid":326269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:33:03.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdf22f6a9fc217213eb0c9c89467b518b121e1aa","tid":1738061,"uid":59548,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:41:14.000Z","msg":"請大家踴躍d做問卷, 同埋一定要答投禮義廉 , 等佢地以為自己好夠票。"},{"pid":"1da49616d544ee375172678fd8dfc3ed748d2b89","tid":1738061,"uid":326269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cdf22f6a9fc217213eb0c9c89467b518b121e1aa","tid":1738061,"uid":59548,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:41:14.000Z","msg":"請大家踴躍d做問卷, 同埋一定要答投禮義廉 , 等佢地以為自己好夠票。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:45:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />年齡組別,社會階層仲有上屆投咩都記得答下"},{"pid":"b08b028c1a8dc028f61f654fd90102df59afdf98","tid":1738061,"uid":326269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:45:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />P牌推唔郁"},{"pid":"9fe41fe99d38e683b8fa2a8cfa376e71d4755318","tid":1738061,"uid":326269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:45:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />P牌推唔郁"},{"pid":"b870d79dc44deba38dc2b427ac2588599a954a69","tid":1738061,"uid":326269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:45:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />P牌推唔郁"},{"pid":"1b5814ddde21f7c48cb1ee9e0b099e57a248f644","tid":1738061,"uid":59548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:48:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02ccd272dcb6834302353fe54c45dc95c87db6d4","tid":1738061,"uid":292644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:49:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">whatsapp收到呢壇野,有冇人知真假?<br />\n---------------------------------------<br />\n工聯會剛發出給會員的內部指引，叫人支持建制派的候選人， 可以用來踢爆哪些假獨立的人士！</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z97E0xt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz97E0xt.png&h=5cab2466&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nLgiwD8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnLgiwD8.png&h=fec2e727&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/57e79qP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F57e79qP.png&h=eae4b54d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zg8Ef5P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzg8Ef5P.png&h=3bb8fe25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rUu0KZa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrUu0KZa.png&h=3e63652e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FgjzPqR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFgjzPqR.png&h=75fff7fc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"abc91c0cb23a5338f3f737c1f94c2de53f5d0386","tid":1738061,"uid":300697,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"25d66fe2ef8eeccc57ce2e952e3805cff0ce4751","tid":1738061,"uid":326269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:29:40.000Z","msg":"選舉通常都會有所謂問卷調查，而做問卷調查嘅機構於2015年嘅區選被報章踢爆「疑似」為建制數票<br />\n<br />\n而<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">唔做問卷係唔可以防止到建制數票</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\nSource: <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20151122/54455653\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20151122%2F54455653&d=U%2B24RsvDmKluq6DDuV4MqrP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=54afe295\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20151122%2F54455653&h=063dc134\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20151122/54455653</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日獲准於票站外進行票站調查的機構當中，香港研究協會、香港社會監察及香港社區研究中心均曾被指與建制派有密切關係，2012年立法會選舉時更有市民號召杯葛這些票站調查。香港研究協會現任會長徐子龍雖不為人熟悉，但<strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">前會長、江蘇省政協委員蘇祉祺</span></strong>身兼「香港新一代文化協會」總幹事，該會更獲<strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">教育局局長吳克儉</span></strong>等任榮譽顧問。 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1039194\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1039194&d=U%2B24RsvDmKluq6DDuV4MqrP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=39f6c5b0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1039194&h=b6ef448d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1039194</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">剛過去的區議會選舉，選舉事務處核准了<span style=\"color: purple;\">四個機構</span>於票站範圍內進行意見調查，這四個機構分別為<strong>港大民意研究計劃，<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">香港研究協會，香港社會監察及香港社區研究中心</span></span></strong>。蘋果日報和明報都曾先後有關於即時的票站調查結果可能會被作為配票之用的報導1。蘋果日報並將港大以外的<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">其餘三者形容為「與建制派有密切關係」</span></span>。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.speakout.hk/%E6%A8%99%E7%B1%A4/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E5%8D%94%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.speakout.hk%2F%25E6%25A8%2599%25E7%25B1%25A4%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A9%25B6%25E5%258D%2594%25E6%259C%2583&d=U%2B24RsvDmKluq6DDuV4MqrP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=42fd0256\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.speakout.hk/%E6%A8%99%E7%B1%A4/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E5%8D%94%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">港人講地直頭有個Label係俾呢間機構<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n根據其中一間嘅網站入面嘅資料所得，佢個問卷調查準確度甚高<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">（我求其Cap佢所謂焦點選區嘅調查資料俾大家睇吓）</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YWPv58L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYWPv58L.png&h=9a6a879a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢喺個調查報告係咁樣寫：<br />\n焦點20個選區入面有14個選區同調查結果乎合，即係至少有<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">70%準確</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n再睇佢問卷入面所問嘅問題<br />\n1. 投票原因（知名度、政綱、背景／立場、形象、過往工作表現）<br />\n2. 選民背景資料（性別、年齡、教育程度、社會階層）<br />\n3. 上次投票取向<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bE1a6dn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbE1a6dn.png&h=5ae77637&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5hZTjyn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5hZTjyn.png&h=1229d059&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zByMEyy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzByMEyy.png&h=fe192da4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺2015年嘅數字入面對家可以計得到咩年齡層、教育程度、社會階層嘅人會偏向投邊一個黨派嘅候選人<br />\n即使唔答任何問卷都好，其實佢地都可以<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">根據外貌分析選民年齡性別</span></strong></span>，點樣都可以達到一定嘅統計紀錄<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">（雖然今年登記選民嘅人數破記錄，但對家有多年嘅數據作參考係不容忽視）</span><br />\n<br />\n所以<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>拒答唔係一個好嘅方法</strong></span><br />\n解決方法係：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">亂答</span></strong></span><br />\n佢地冇權查你身份證，姐係話你咩<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">年紀</span></span>佢唔會知<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">（性別就冇得呃喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">教育程度、社會階層、上次投票取向</span></span>對方都冇機會Check到係咪準確<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：我都係鳩睇報告並非專業，有錯歡迎大家一齊探討<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">雖然選舉並非能救全家，但兄弟爬山<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n伸延閱讀：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1725914/\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1725914/</a><br />\n[區選] 區選相關策略<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1701333/\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1701333/</a><br />\n[區選]文宣圖及相關整合"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:51:44.000Z","msg":"我會話自己投保皇黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"044074a473aefeac2e86e8b2fdc30ec8074ebc0f","tid":1738061,"uid":229920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:51:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ee00e63d9420f111a81b1538ba7ac7615759163","tid":1738061,"uid":150053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:57:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed87c1c48e266401f6c6705e11870dcf185a1101","tid":1738061,"uid":150053,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"abc91c0cb23a5338f3f737c1f94c2de53f5d0386","tid":1738061,"uid":300697,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"25d66fe2ef8eeccc57ce2e952e3805cff0ce4751","tid":1738061,"uid":326269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:29:40.000Z","msg":"選舉通常都會有所謂問卷調查，而做問卷調查嘅機構於2015年嘅區選被報章踢爆「疑似」為建制數票<br />\n<br />\n而<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">唔做問卷係唔可以防止到建制數票</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\nSource: <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20151122/54455653\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20151122%2F54455653&d=U%2B24RsvDmKluq6DDuV4MqrP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=54afe295\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20151122%2F54455653&h=063dc134\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20151122/54455653</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日獲准於票站外進行票站調查的機構當中，香港研究協會、香港社會監察及香港社區研究中心均曾被指與建制派有密切關係，2012年立法會選舉時更有市民號召杯葛這些票站調查。香港研究協會現任會長徐子龍雖不為人熟悉，但<strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">前會長、江蘇省政協委員蘇祉祺</span></strong>身兼「香港新一代文化協會」總幹事，該會更獲<strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">教育局局長吳克儉</span></strong>等任榮譽顧問。 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1039194\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1039194&d=U%2B24RsvDmKluq6DDuV4MqrP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=39f6c5b0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1039194&h=b6ef448d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1039194</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">剛過去的區議會選舉，選舉事務處核准了<span style=\"color: purple;\">四個機構</span>於票站範圍內進行意見調查，這四個機構分別為<strong>港大民意研究計劃，<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">香港研究協會，香港社會監察及香港社區研究中心</span></span></strong>。蘋果日報和明報都曾先後有關於即時的票站調查結果可能會被作為配票之用的報導1。蘋果日報並將港大以外的<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">其餘三者形容為「與建制派有密切關係」</span></span>。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.speakout.hk/%E6%A8%99%E7%B1%A4/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E5%8D%94%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.speakout.hk%2F%25E6%25A8%2599%25E7%25B1%25A4%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A9%25B6%25E5%258D%2594%25E6%259C%2583&d=U%2B24RsvDmKluq6DDuV4MqrP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=42fd0256\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.speakout.hk/%E6%A8%99%E7%B1%A4/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E5%8D%94%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">港人講地直頭有個Label係俾呢間機構<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n根據其中一間嘅網站入面嘅資料所得，佢個問卷調查準確度甚高<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">（我求其Cap佢所謂焦點選區嘅調查資料俾大家睇吓）</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YWPv58L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYWPv58L.png&h=9a6a879a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢喺個調查報告係咁樣寫：<br />\n焦點20個選區入面有14個選區同調查結果乎合，即係至少有<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">70%準確</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n再睇佢問卷入面所問嘅問題<br />\n1. 投票原因（知名度、政綱、背景／立場、形象、過往工作表現）<br />\n2. 選民背景資料（性別、年齡、教育程度、社會階層）<br />\n3. 上次投票取向<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bE1a6dn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbE1a6dn.png&h=5ae77637&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5hZTjyn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5hZTjyn.png&h=1229d059&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zByMEyy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzByMEyy.png&h=fe192da4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺2015年嘅數字入面對家可以計得到咩年齡層、教育程度、社會階層嘅人會偏向投邊一個黨派嘅候選人<br />\n即使唔答任何問卷都好，其實佢地都可以<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">根據外貌分析選民年齡性別</span></strong></span>，點樣都可以達到一定嘅統計紀錄<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">（雖然今年登記選民嘅人數破記錄，但對家有多年嘅數據作參考係不容忽視）</span><br />\n<br />\n所以<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>拒答唔係一個好嘅方法</strong></span><br />\n解決方法係：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">亂答</span></strong></span><br />\n佢地冇權查你身份證，姐係話你咩<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">年紀</span></span>佢唔會知<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">（性別就冇得呃喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">教育程度、社會階層、上次投票取向</span></span>對方都冇機會Check到係咪準確<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：我都係鳩睇報告並非專業，有錯歡迎大家一齊探討<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">雖然選舉並非能救全家，但兄弟爬山<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n伸延閱讀：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1725914/\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1725914/</a><br />\n[區選] 區選相關策略<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1701333/\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1701333/</a><br />\n[區選]文宣圖及相關整合"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:51:44.000Z","msg":"我會話自己投保皇黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:58:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家都是「投」建制"},{"pid":"e7217bf501f18f38f21f2e1c06f61f50bf01528b","tid":1738061,"uid":150053,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:58:58.000Z","msg":"我今年都40歲喇，做清潔工人，投建制，年年都係投建制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"710bc008071f836062b20f13b0ba8d870ceb697a","tid":1738061,"uid":150053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:59:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"413636a7e2bc2990655090fd99868ac0a6dd5a33","tid":1738061,"uid":272030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T07:02:07.000Z","msg":"泛民區議會選舉前快啲做野<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1737778\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1737778</a><br />\n<br />\n麻煩幫手推"},{"pid":"d2e68ab389566a397f2eeff6e993a76de97e3d34","tid":1738061,"uid":150053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"413636a7e2bc2990655090fd99868ac0a6dd5a33","tid":1738061,"uid":272030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T07:02:07.000Z","msg":"泛民區議會選舉前快啲做野<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1737778\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1737778</a><br />\n<br />\n麻煩幫手推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T07:03:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f7a326d956112cfa0c955ebb971d18f39bb8fe6","tid":1738061,"uid":150053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T07:04:10.000Z","msg":"任何有機會嘅嘢都要一試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4583a99e2d8af73339f6642b05a9c3c5b26fac7d","tid":1738061,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T07:04:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c012e4ab919d4f52338caa9c9f84a5953cb85104","tid":1738061,"